<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧١٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/13865">‌يُونُسُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">‌قَتَادَةَ </a>، <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/0">‌عَمَّنْ </a>سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">‌أَبَا هُرَيْرَةَ </a>،<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">«كَانَ رَسُولُ اللهِ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ ضَخْمَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣١٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>الْكَفَّيْنِ، ضَخْمَ الْقَدَمَيْنِ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>